      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model with nonlinear geometry (NLGEOM) applied. Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) elastic modulus and yield strength sourced from ASTM F136 material certification data. Augmented Lagrangian contact formulation used for screw-block interface, consistent with literature precedent for F1717 FEA. Model form appropriate for compression-bending QoIs at required level 3."
