      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load rate (5 mm/min) and ambient temperature per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition was evaluated; the required level 3 calls for at least two distinct test conditions to characterize condition sensitivity. This factor is below the required level and represents a noted gap in the validation evidence. Risk accepted given the standardized nature of the F1717 protocol and the medium model risk level."
